      <title>加拿大央行麦克勒姆：六月有可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/bank-of-canada-s-macklem-june-rate-cut-a-possibility-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂夫·麦克勒姆表示，央行在降息之前需要更多证据证明通胀正在放缓。加拿大央行连续第六次会议维持政策利率不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/bank-of-canada-s-macklem-june-rate-cut-a-possibility-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
