      <title>由于通胀进展停滞，美联储面临降息的“软期限”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fed-rate-cut-plan-clouded-as-inflation-progress-stalls-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储降低通胀之路上的坎坷看起来更像是一个障碍，让人对其今年的降息计划产生怀疑。]]></description>
